//About use page This application is developed by John Alvin Joseph,for the purpose of Remotely Diagnosing A Car. The application allows the users to monitor real-time vehicle data as well as scanning for Diagnostic Fault Codes. This application is developed for my Degree Final Year Project.This application requires the users to purchase a ELM327 device or any OBD compatible tool.The system connects to the tool using Bluetooth connection. Hence, users are required to connect to the device beforehand through the Bluetooth Settings terminal in their mobile devices. The system communicates to the device using AT commands to request and receive data regarding the vehicle. Users can contact the developer through email if there is any bugs found while using the system or provide suggestions on further improvement. Email:johnalvin04gmail.com
